entry.string:
echo "Instalando dependencias necesarias..." apt-get update apt-get install -y apt-transport-https ca-certificates curl gnupg lsb-release
echo "Configurando repositorio de Docker..." install -m 0755 -d /etc/apt/keyrings curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | gpg --dearmor -o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg chmod a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg echo "deb [arch=$(dpkg --print-architecture) signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu $(lsb_release -cs) stable" | tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list > /dev/null
echo "Instalando Docker..." apt-get update apt-get install -y docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-buildx-plugin docker-compose-plugin
echo "Verificando instalación de Docker..." docker --version
